head_commit.message:
Optimise package installation (#153)

Significantly reduce the build time and storage of vcpkg packages by
removing ubsan-specific packages and removing dependency on llvm.

* Remove specialised triplets for ubsan
* Remove ubsan job from Build-Packages workflow
* Update package versions to latest
* Exclude TryCompile errors from logfile output
* Restrict vcpkg log output in CI to those reported as errors
* Make update packages script update to latest release instead of latest
master
* Update Swiftshader to latest master
* Use Subzero instead of LLVM as Swiftshader reactor backend
* Simplify Swiftshader patch
* Update VMA port
* Add script for determining vcpkg hash
